    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to given sets of written works, together with a particular set of conventions for their use. Distinct from "alphabets" which are sets of characters or symbols with which a language is written, not including a set of conventions for their use.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
